228
00:12:04,260 --> 00:12:05,620
The higher-ups won't forgive you!

229
00:12:12,700 --> 00:12:14,100
I'll bear the consequences of today.

230
00:12:17,420 --> 00:12:18,860
There's something I must do,

231
00:12:20,860 --> 00:12:22,580
